_sText:
Hi guys! This is my first map for CS:S and my first submission to Gamebanana. This map was made entirely by me in 10 hours non-stop (believe me)

Intermission

This map is located somewhere in Italy. It is a storage for most of museums in Italy. Terrorists need to blow up one of the spots in storage to destroy many valuable artefacts.

I'm probably not going to update this map. If you want to make this map for CS:GO, please credit me as an original creator.
